341
00:22:28,187 --> 00:22:29,770
Cepat berangkat.

342
00:22:29,770 --> 00:22:31,790
Jangan menunda pertandingan
Akademi Master Roh.

343
00:22:35,090 --> 00:22:37,610
Menantang yang kuat,
